1
00:00:12,240 --> 00:00:13,080
You broke the rules.

2
00:00:15,800 --> 00:00:16,520
Did I?

3
00:00:24,240 --> 00:00:25,000
What about you?

4
00:00:26,200 --> 00:00:26,800
Tian Yan.

5
00:00:27,760 --> 00:00:28,480
What?

6
00:00:30,120 --> 00:00:31,280
Is your heart

7
00:00:32,440 --> 00:00:33,680
beating fast?

8
00:00:43,800 --> 00:00:44,840
Are you satisfied

9
00:00:45,680 --> 00:00:46,480
with this answer?

10
00:01:00,400 --> 00:01:01,160
Tian Yan.

11
00:01:01,720 --> 00:01:03,040
If you betray me,

12
00:01:05,200 --> 00:01:06,560
I will hate you to death.

13
00:01:07,280 --> 00:01:08,480
If one day

14
00:01:08,600 --> 00:01:10,320
I find out you betrayed me,

15
00:01:10,600 --> 00:01:13,640
I will make you suffer terribly.

16
00:01:43,080 --> 00:01:44,760
Where is my dad?

17
00:01:48,960 --> 00:01:50,280
Where did he go?

18
00:01:53,320 --> 00:01:54,600
I sent him away.

19
00:01:55,400 --> 00:01:56,480
Don't worry.

20
00:01:56,480 --> 00:01:57,680
He's still breathing.

21
00:02:10,560 --> 00:02:11,760
I told you.

22
00:02:13,400 --> 00:02:14,360
leave it to me.

23
00:02:26,120 --> 00:02:28,200
I'll never let anyone bully you again.

24
00:02:29,040 --> 00:02:30,120
From today on,

25
00:02:31,440 --> 00:02:32,320
you're free.

26
00:02:39,080 --> 00:02:40,160
I'll never...

27
00:02:41,880 --> 00:02:43,840
I'll never be free in my life.

28
00:02:51,960 --> 00:02:53,000
You don't need this

29
00:02:54,920 --> 00:02:56,120
when you're by my side.

30
00:03:04,480 --> 00:03:05,880
Tianyan is the only person

31
00:03:07,040 --> 00:03:09,560
who has been good to me since childhood.

32
00:03:12,280 --> 00:03:13,720
Can you promise me

33
00:03:15,040 --> 00:03:16,200
not to hurt her?

34
00:03:18,680 --> 00:03:19,200
Okay.

35
00:03:20,320 --> 00:03:21,360
I promise you.

36
00:03:35,440 --> 00:03:36,200
Obedience Water.

37
00:03:38,640 --> 00:03:40,480
The jade factories of the Fengyue Villa and the Silver Light Hall

38
00:03:40,480 --> 00:03:41,280
are connected underground.

39
00:03:42,320 --> 00:03:43,640
They make workers do drug experiments

40
00:03:43,640 --> 00:03:44,720
to force them

41
00:03:44,720 --> 00:03:45,960
to work day and night.

42
00:03:46,760 --> 00:03:47,640
It's too cruel.

43
00:03:48,800 --> 00:03:49,240
So,

44
00:03:49,280 --> 00:03:50,160
what happened

45
00:03:50,800 --> 00:03:52,080
to those workers?

46
00:03:52,520 --> 00:03:53,280
What do you think?

47
00:03:54,040 --> 00:03:55,000
They were physically exhausted.

48
00:03:55,040 --> 00:03:55,600
Just like

49
00:03:55,720 --> 00:03:56,720
a dead horse.

50
00:03:57,280 --> 00:03:58,600
This kind of evil practice

51
00:03:58,800 --> 00:03:59,920
was created by

52
00:04:00,960 --> 00:04:02,920
Ouyang Qing and Pang Jingfu.

53
00:04:03,560 --> 00:04:04,480
They are not human.

54
00:04:08,160 --> 00:04:10,200
When will you arrest them

55
00:04:10,600 --> 00:04:12,080
and destroy the Fengyue Villa?

56
00:04:12,520 --> 00:04:13,840
I'm waiting for your decision.

57
00:04:31,920 --> 00:04:32,520
Father,

58
00:04:35,240 --> 00:04:36,000
are you looking for me?

59
00:04:36,440 --> 00:04:37,320
Afu,

60
00:04:37,600 --> 00:04:38,520
long time no see.

61
00:04:41,720 --> 00:04:43,160
I can't get in touch with you.

62
00:04:43,840 --> 00:04:44,920
How are you doing lately?

63
00:04:48,600 --> 00:04:49,920
I've been in business for so many years,

64
00:04:50,760 --> 00:04:51,680
I've made more enemies

65
00:04:51,720 --> 00:04:52,600
than friends.

66
00:04:54,640 --> 00:04:55,840
Now, even dying peacefully

67
00:04:55,840 --> 00:04:57,800
in my own bed is hard.

68
00:04:59,040 --> 00:05:00,040
Sometimes I feel

69
00:05:00,120 --> 00:05:01,240
like a mouse,

70
00:05:02,040 --> 00:05:04,480
only safe when hiding in different holes.

71
00:05:10,480 --> 00:05:11,280
Come, sit.

72
00:05:14,960 --> 00:05:15,920
I'll stand

73
00:05:16,920 --> 00:05:17,880
and listen to your words.

74
00:05:25,480 --> 00:05:27,000
I've reviewed the accounts of the Silver Light Hall.

75
00:05:28,040 --> 00:05:28,600
Very good.

76
00:05:30,440 --> 00:05:31,640
Better than I expected.

77
00:05:32,400 --> 00:05:33,080
That's what I should do.

78
00:05:35,560 --> 00:05:37,160
As for Siqing,

79
00:05:40,720 --> 00:05:42,200
I've given him many chances,

80
00:05:43,200 --> 00:05:44,160
but he didn't seize any of them.

81
00:05:44,680 --> 00:05:46,160
He didn't focus on the right track,

82
00:05:46,600 --> 00:05:47,920
always playing tricks,

83
00:05:48,520 --> 00:05:50,040
and tattling to his mother.

84
00:05:50,440 --> 00:05:51,960
If the Silver Light Hall

85
00:05:52,640 --> 00:05:54,080
encounters some difficulties,

86
00:05:55,680 --> 00:05:56,760
he can't steer the ship,

87
00:05:58,880 --> 00:05:59,920
you have to.

88
00:06:02,800 --> 00:06:03,400
I know

89
00:06:03,880 --> 00:06:05,480
you have a grudge against me.

90
00:06:05,960 --> 00:06:07,240
I'm sorry for what happened

91
00:06:08,000 --> 00:06:09,640
to your mother.

92
00:06:10,400 --> 00:06:12,240
But what could I do?

93
00:06:12,360 --> 00:06:13,880
If IPCO had investigated her,

94
00:06:14,040 --> 00:06:15,000
she would have been in prison for a few years.

95
00:06:15,000 --> 00:06:15,560
Dad,

96
00:06:20,360 --> 00:06:21,520
it's all over.

97
00:06:30,280 --> 00:06:31,360
It's good that

98
00:06:34,160 --> 00:06:34,760
you can think so.

99
00:06:36,680 --> 00:06:38,440
Mercy is a death warrant,

100
00:06:38,600 --> 00:06:40,040
and hesitation is a boning knife.

101
00:06:40,560 --> 00:06:41,240
It seems that

102
00:06:41,640 --> 00:06:43,360
you understand these earlier than me.

103
00:06:45,000 --> 00:06:45,880
I'm getting old.

104
00:06:47,000 --> 00:06:48,960
My body is getting worse.

105
00:07:02,280 --> 00:07:03,160
Take this.

106
00:07:04,280 --> 00:07:05,840
If there are any important documents in the future,

107
00:07:06,400 --> 00:07:07,120
you can sign it yourself,

108
00:07:07,760 --> 00:07:09,000
no need to go through me.

109
00:07:12,040 --> 00:07:12,720
Afu,

110
00:07:14,040 --> 00:07:15,680
I'm leaving the Silver Light Hall to you.

111
00:07:20,280 --> 00:07:21,280
Don't let me down.

112
00:07:25,400 --> 00:07:25,840
Come,

113
00:07:26,160 --> 00:07:27,040
sit with me for a while.

114
00:07:37,680 --> 00:07:38,600
Old man,

115
00:07:39,160 --> 00:07:42,000
you're really going to give everything to that bastard.

116
00:07:43,080 --> 00:07:43,800
Good,

117
00:07:44,640 --> 00:07:45,520
very good.

118
00:07:46,160 --> 00:07:46,960
Grandma,

119
00:07:47,680 --> 00:07:48,560
you know what?

120
00:07:49,280 --> 00:07:50,760
I met someone

121
00:07:50,800 --> 00:07:52,080
special recently.

122
00:07:52,760 --> 00:07:54,520
He sees through my disguise

123
00:07:55,280 --> 00:07:56,840
and knows my thoughts.

124
00:07:57,320 --> 00:07:58,840
He talks tough,

125
00:07:59,040 --> 00:07:59,680
but

126
00:08:03,600 --> 00:08:05,840
agrees to all my requests unconditionally.

127
00:08:09,040 --> 00:08:10,040
He once

128
00:08:10,880 --> 00:08:11,800
blocked a knife for me,

129
00:08:13,080 --> 00:08:14,360
celebrated my birthday with me,

130
00:08:15,920 --> 00:08:16,800
and

131
00:08:18,480 --> 00:08:20,480
carefully repaired the things

132
00:08:21,360 --> 00:08:23,560
I used to trick him,

133
00:08:23,640 --> 00:08:25,600
giving them to me as treasures.

134
00:08:33,040 --> 00:08:34,200
But he killed my master

135
00:08:35,880 --> 00:08:37,800
and did many cruel things.

136
00:08:45,120 --> 00:08:46,560
I kept telling myself

137
00:08:47,040 --> 00:08:48,080
that what I did was right.

138
00:08:48,080 --> 00:08:49,360
I was uncovering the truth,

139
00:08:50,200 --> 00:08:51,520
avenging my master,

140
00:08:51,600 --> 00:08:53,480
I'm preventing more tragedies from happening.

141
00:08:57,200 --> 00:08:57,800
Am I right?

142
00:08:59,160 --> 00:08:59,920
Grandma.

143
00:09:02,040 --> 00:09:03,360
What I did is right.

144
00:09:03,560 --> 00:09:04,240
Right?

145
00:09:08,160 --> 00:09:09,960
Grandma, what should I do?

146
00:09:11,800 --> 00:09:13,400
I have no one to talk to.

147
00:09:14,200 --> 00:09:16,160
I can't tell him.

148
00:09:29,520 --> 00:09:30,200
Doctor.

149
00:09:31,320 --> 00:09:32,240
Thank you.

150
00:09:32,840 --> 00:09:33,920
It's okay. My duty.

151
00:09:50,000 --> 00:09:51,160
[What can't you]

152
00:09:51,760 --> 00:09:52,520
[tell me?]

153
00:10:01,240 --> 00:10:02,040
[Pang Jingfu,]

154
00:10:03,400 --> 00:10:04,360
[let's go on a date.]

155
00:10:08,280 --> 00:10:09,280
[Just like]

156
00:10:09,960 --> 00:10:11,240
[a normal couple.]

157
00:10:11,720 --> 00:10:12,400
[Date?]

158
00:10:13,120 --> 00:10:13,680
[The day after tomorrow.]

159
00:10:14,400 --> 00:10:15,040
[Okay?]

160
00:10:19,320 --> 00:10:19,760
[Okay.]

161
00:10:26,800 --> 00:10:27,400
Tian Yan,

162
00:10:28,480 --> 00:10:29,280
I know

163
00:10:31,200 --> 00:10:32,560
you won't lie to me again.

164
00:10:38,280 --> 00:10:39,880
Two days later, we'll take actions in batches.

165
00:10:40,240 --> 00:10:42,120
One group will take down the Fengyue Villa

166
00:10:42,360 --> 00:10:43,400
and arrest Ouyang Qing.

167
00:10:43,800 --> 00:10:44,600
Another group,

168
00:10:45,280 --> 00:10:47,400
led by 237 Tian Yan,

169
00:10:47,680 --> 00:10:49,200
will cooperate to arrest Pang Jingfu.

170
00:11:08,400 --> 00:11:10,640
Everything will be over after the day after tomorrow.

171
00:11:14,480 --> 00:11:15,400
Pang Jingfu,

172
00:11:16,520 --> 00:11:18,440
let me lie to you one last time.
